{"tid":905685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【連環殺手】加州罪犯自爆曾殺90人 或成美國史上最恐怖殺人犯","createTime":"2018-11-17T10:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T11:59:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bdbf1bcfaf106aee7246a0713a6d7da0314028bd","tid":905685,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"(北美通訊)加州一名因三宗謀殺案而入獄的犯人Samuel Little，周四承認自己涉及約90宗殺人事件，他對其中逾三分之一案件的陳述，已獲檢察機構證實並無虛假。若Little確實犯下他聲稱的所有案件，將成為美國史上殺人數量最多的連環殺手。<br />\n現年78歲的Little，過去曾是拳擊手，有吸毒、搶劫、入侵民居等前科，犯罪足跡遍布24個州，最早於16歲因入屋盜竊被捕。2014年，他因3宗加州女子謀殺案被定罪，當時負責訴訟的檢察官表示，Little至少須對1980年代以來、全國40宗殺人案負責。<br />\nLittle今年9月被押送至德州，接受其他數州的執法人員盤問。他近日向德州公安部巡警James Holland承認，1994年殺死一名德州女子，之後又坦承在1970年至2005年間，曾犯下數十宗謀殺案。德州厄克托縣檢察官Bobby Bland表示，Little對超過30宗案件的描述「無誤」。他稱，Little可能因為終身監禁上訴失敗，自覺不再需要隱瞞罪行，所以「自爆」。<br />\n當年查案的洛杉磯警探認為，Little的犯罪型態符合連環殺手（serial killer）特徵，極可能涉及更多謀殺案。Little特別針對女性，經常先將女性打昏，邊自慰邊掐死她們，然後棄屍逃走。<br />\n如果Little確實犯下約90宗謀殺案，他將成為已偵破案件中、殺人數量最多的連環兇手。資料顯示，有兩名連環殺手承認於1970年代，各犯下超過30宗凶案，分別為Ted Bundy和John Wayne Gacy。前者最終被電擊處死，後者則被執行毒針死刑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542429279_b686.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542429279_b686.jpg&h=3acc1b26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181117/58924383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58924383&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=ba194584\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58924383&h=4dcdc5f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181117/58924383</a>"},{"pid":"be6811a88970197f3b51d45bd15708ac41fccacd","tid":905685,"uid":22913,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:40:35.000Z","msg":"邊自慰邊掐死她<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c3d64025821fb1d0140ce66ff7e6ad485bfd8c","tid":905685,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:46:26.000Z","msg":"殺咁多人仲記得咁清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7051be5af7559f002533d77c0056a81f860bdb","tid":905685,"uid":45213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:48:08.000Z","msg":"高手"},{"pid":"8a88804381b17ce6262de457227c193ff3b62558","tid":905685,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:48:40.000Z","msg":"為何不姦："},{"pid":"619a679643e9787934245eaa79c93c985e3edd8b","tid":905685,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:49:22.000Z","msg":"Michael Meyer"},{"pid":"c39ed3400544290d87cfa4cebc179028898cc74e","tid":905685,"uid":191956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:52:49.000Z","msg":"辣殺黎 暈左準備個套直撚接屌啦 仲打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee9bf50a37425323fc4e1e503c89c78aaa6c8b7","tid":905685,"uid":143582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:00:21.000Z","msg":"為咗打個飛機殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4706222cd301bec6312d223845cad321583fde92","tid":905685,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16c3d64025821fb1d0140ce66ff7e6ad485bfd8c","tid":905685,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:46:26.000Z","msg":"殺咁多人仲記得咁清楚<img src=\"/assets/f